{"id": "webh_profile", "modality": "web", "name": "Profile", "task": {"description": "Build a social profile page for '@maya.codes' at 1920px wide. A full-width cover banner, with a circular avatar overlapping its bottom edge, the display name 'Maya Chen', handle, and a bio line. A stats row of THREE equal-width items (Posts 248, Followers 12.4k, Following 386) with a 'Follow' button. A tab bar (Posts, Media, Likes) with Posts active. Below, a responsive post grid of at least 9 equal-size square thumbnail placeholders in 3 columns with uniform gaps. Responsive: at 375px the stats row stays in one line (smaller), and the post grid becomes 1 column (or stays a tight grid) without horizontal overflow.", "requirements": ["A full-width cover banner with a circular avatar overlapping its bottom edge", "The display name, handle, and a bio line are present and legible over/under the banner", "A stats row shows three equal-width items (Posts 248, Followers 12.4k, Following 386) plus a Follow button", "A tab bar shows Posts, Media, Likes with Posts visibly active", "The post grid shows at least 9 equal-size square thumbnails in 3 columns with uniform gaps", "The avatar is circular and does not overlap the name/stats text", "Thumbnails are uniformly sized and aligned in a clean grid (no ragged last row gaps misaligning the columns)", "On desktop nothing overflows horizontally", "At 375px the layout has no horizontal overflow and the stats row remains on one line", "A single accent color is reused for the active tab, the Follow button, and links"], "difficulty": "hard"}, "runs": [{"run": 1, "ss_n_defects": 0, "ss_text_overlap": null, "ss_clipped": null, "ss_overflow": null, "ss_total_tokens": 3250, "rv_n_defects": 0, "rv_text_overlap": null, "rv_clipped": null, "rv_overflow": null, "rv_iterations": 1, "rv_total_tokens": 3290}, {"run": 2, "ss_n_defects": 2, "ss_text_overlap": null, "ss_clipped": null, "ss_overflow": null, "ss_total_tokens": 3081, "rv_n_defects": 5, "rv_text_overlap": null, "rv_clipped": null, "rv_overflow": null, "rv_iterations": 3, "rv_total_tokens": 14271}, {"run": 3, "ss_n_defects": 0, "ss_text_overlap": null, "ss_clipped": null, "ss_overflow": null, "ss_total_tokens": 3065, "rv_n_defects": 7, "rv_text_overlap": null, "rv_clipped": null, "rv_overflow": null, "rv_iterations": 3, "rv_total_tokens": 14242}], "ss_img": "images/web/webh_profile_ss.jpg", "rv_img": "images/web/webh_profile_rv.jpg", "ss_html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>@maya.codes - Maya Chen</title>\n    <style>\n        * {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;\n            background-color: #fafafa;\n            color: #262626;\n            line-height: 1.5;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            max-width: 1920px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            background-color: white;\n            min-height: 100vh;\n        }\n\n        /* Cover Banner */\n        .cover-banner {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 320px;\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);\n            position: relative;\n            margin-bottom: 80px;\n        }\n\n        /* Avatar */\n        .avatar {\n            width: 160px;\n            height: 160px;\n            border-radius: 50%;\n            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #ff6b6b, #4ecdc4);\n            border: 6px solid white;\n            position: absolute;\n            bottom: -80px;\n            left: 50%;\n            transform: translateX(-50%);\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            justify-content: center;\n            font-size: 48px;\n            font-weight: 700;\n            color: white;\n            text-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);\n        }\n\n        /* Profile Info */\n        .profile-info {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 0 40px;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n        }\n\n        .display-name {\n            font-size: 32px;\n            font-weight: 700;\n            color: #262626;\n            margin-bottom: 8px;\n        }\n\n        .handle {\n            font-size: 18px;\n            color: #8e8e8e;\n            margin-bottom: 16px;\n        }\n\n        .bio {\n            font-size: 16px;\n            color: #262626;\n            max-width: 600px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n        }\n\n        /* Stats Row */\n        .stats-section {\n            padding: 0 40px;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n        }\n\n        .stats-row {\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            justify-content: center;\n            gap: 60px;\n            margin-bottom: 32px;\n        }\n\n        .stat-item {\n            text-align: center;\n            flex: 0 0 auto;\n        }\n\n        .stat-number {\n            font-size: 24px;\n            font-weight: 700;\n            color: #262626;\n            display: block;\n            margin-bottom: 4px;\n        }\n\n        .stat-label {\n            font-size: 16px;\n            color: #8e8e8e;\n        }\n\n        .follow-button {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);\n            color: white;\n            border: none;\n            padding: 12px 32px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            font-size: 16px;\n            font-weight: 600;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;\n        }\n\n        .follow-button:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-2px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.3);\n        }\n\n        /* Tab Bar */\n        .tab-bar {\n            border-bottom: 1px solid #dbdbdb;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n        }\n\n        .tab-list {\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            gap: 60px;\n            padding: 0 40px;\n        }\n\n        .tab-item {\n            padding: 16px 0;\n            font-size: 16px;\n            font-weight: 600;\n            color: #8e8e8e;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-bottom: 2px solid transparent;\n            transition: all 0.2s ease;\n        }\n\n        .tab-item.active {\n            color: #262626;\n            border-bottom-color: #667eea;\n        }\n\n        .tab-item:hover {\n            color: #262626;\n        }\n\n        /* Post Grid */\n        .post-grid {\n            padding: 0 40px 40px;\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);\n            gap: 20px;\n            max-width: 1200px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n        }\n\n        .post-thumbnail {\n            aspect-ratio: 1;\n            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #f0f0f0, #e0e0e0);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            justify-content: center;\n            font-size: 18px;\n            color: #8e8e8e;\n            transition: transform 0.2s ease;\n            cursor: pointer;\n        }\n\n        .post-thumbnail:hover {\n            transform: scale(1.02);\n        }\n\n        .post-thumbnail:nth-child(3n+1) {\n            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #ff9a9e, #fecfef);\n        }\n\n        .post-thumbnail:nth-child(3n+2) {\n            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #a8edea, #fed6e3);\n        }\n\n        .post-thumbnail:nth-child(3n+3) {\n            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #ffecd2, #fcb69f);\n        }\n\n        /* Mobile Responsive */\n        @media (max-width: 375px) {\n            .cover-banner {\n                height: 200px;\n                margin-bottom: 60px;\n            }\n\n            .avatar {\n                width: 120px;\n   